      "id": "cancel_membership",
      "question": "How do I cancel my membership?",
      "answer": "You can cancel anytime from your account settings. Go to Settings → Membership → Manage plan and click “Cancel membership”. Your access will continue until the end of your current billing period. You will receive a confirmation email once the cancellation is processed.",
