      "question": "What is your refund policy?",
      "answer": "For monthly plans we do not offer prorated refunds, but you will keep access until the end of your billing period. For annual plans, we offer a 14-day money-back guarantee on your first purchase. If you’re not satisfied, contact support within 14 days and we’ll refund your payment in full.",
